{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fold. Transform. Create Magic.  <strong>ORIFOLDIUM</strong> is here\u2014a puzzle game where geometry bends to your will. Prepare to challenge reality, one block at a time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244150/extras/store0.gif?t=1737704709\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>ORIFOLDIUM</strong>\u00a0is a mind-bending puzzle game in which you fold geometric blocks into mystical Magick shapes, challenging spatial reasoning and creative thinking.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244150/extras/store1.gif?t=1737704709\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Imagine a world where simple shapes bend to your will, where logical thinking meets mystical transformation. <strong>ORIFOLDIUM</strong> challenges players to fold, manipulate, and create intricate magical configurations that will test the limits of spatial reasoning and creative imagination.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>ORIFOLDIUM</strong> isn't just a game\u2014it's a meditation on transformation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Innovative Gameplay:</strong> Master the art of block folding to create mystical shapes</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Mind-Bending Puzzles:</strong>\u00a013 Progressive challenges that grow with your skills</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Mesmerizing Aesthetic:</strong> Retro color palette meets magical geometric design</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Puzzle editor</strong> with Steam Workshop integration</p